自 2020 年以来，LGBTQ 游戏玩家数量增加了 70% https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/number-of-lgbtq-gamers-has-risen-by-70-per-cent-since-2020-3586714?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=number-自 2020 年以来，LGBTQ 玩家数量增加了 70%Imogen Donovan Tue, 13 Feb 2024 16:37:40 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsNintendo SwitchPCPS4PS5Xbox OneXbox Series X|S https://www.nme.com/?p=3586714 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> GLAAD 表示，游戏与 LGBTQ 代表“不一致”</p><p>自 2020 年首次在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/number-of-lgbtq-gamers-has-risen-by-70-per-cent-since-2020-3586714">以来，LGBTQ 游戏玩家数量增加了 70%</a> 。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> LGBTQ 倡导非营利组织 GLAAD 的首份游戏报告发现，近 20% 的活跃游戏玩家认为自己是女同性恋、男同性恋、双性恋、跨性别者和/或酷儿 (LGBTQ)，但只有不到 3% 的游戏包含 LGBTQ 内容。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/why-tomb-raider-will-always-be-a-core-part-of-my-queer-identity-3062951">为什么“古墓丽影”将永远是我酷儿身份的核心部分</a></strong></li></ul><p>该组织总裁兼首席执行官莎拉·凯特·埃利斯 (Sarah Kate Ellis) 表示：“特别是对于 LGBTQ 游戏玩家来说，游戏不仅是一种逃避和娱乐的来源，也是自我表达的重要渠道。”</p><p> “对于 LGBTQ 游戏玩家来说，他们在自己玩的游戏中看到我们社区的代表，并在与其他游戏玩家交流和表达自己时保持安全，现在已经是过去的事情了。” </p><figure id="attachment_3586739" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3586739" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3586739" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3586739" class="wp-caption-text"> 《博德之门 3》图片来源：Larian Studios</figcaption></figure><p>自 2020 年以来，被认定为 LGBTQ 群体成员的游戏玩家数量增加了 70%。在这一人群中，年轻年龄段的比例有所增加——35 岁以下游戏玩家的比例为 23% 至 28%。</p><p>在各个平台上，LGBTQ 游戏玩家更喜欢开放世界游戏、模拟游戏、角色扮演游戏、恐怖游戏和益智游戏。另一方面，非 LGBTQ 玩家更有可能玩射击游戏。两个群体都同样喜欢冒险、动作角色扮演、格斗和大逃杀游戏。</p><p>就购买偏好而言，LGBTQ 玩家购买或玩游戏的可能性是非 LGBTQ 玩家的 1.4 倍，因为游戏可以让他们扮演与自己性别相匹配的角色。</p><p>然而，GLAAD 于 2023 年 11 月评估了<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/xbox">Xbox</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/playstation">PlayStation</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/nintendo-switch">Nintendo Switch</a>上被标记为包含 LGBTQ 内容的游戏数量。 </p><figure id="attachment_3586741" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3586741" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3586741" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/glaad-survey-finds-one-in-five-gamers-are-LGBTQ-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3586741" class="wp-caption-text">刺客信条：枭雄 图片来源：Ubisoft</figcaption></figure><p>具有此内容标签的游戏​​在 Xbox、PlayStation 和任天堂数字店面提供的游戏名册中所占比例不到 2%。至于<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/steam">Steam</a> ，这一比例略高，不到2.5%。</p><p>报告中写道：“只有不到 2% 的可用游戏包含 LGBTQ 内容，这与当代媒体格格不入，游戏行业辜负了 LGBTQ 消费者和我们的盟友。”</p><p>报告全文可<a href="https://glaad.org/glaad-gaming/2024/">在此处</a>获取。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/silent-hill-second-sacrifice-gets-playable-demo-on-playstation-4-3586687"><em>《寂静岭：第二次牺牲》</em></a>是一款粉丝游戏，由一位独立开发者倾注了四年的心血，并且可以在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/playstation">PS4</a>上玩。</p><p>自 2020 年首次在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/number-of-lgbtq-gamers-has-risen-by-70-per-cent-since-2020-3586714">以来，LGBTQ 游戏玩家数量增加了 70%</a> 。</p> ;
